gitflower (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release: Python rewrite of gitflower (FastAPI + click).
    - Per-repository pre-push hook engine: branch router with
      Go-compatible glob patterns, protected-branch workflows,
      gitflower init/install/uninstall/config.
    - Repo hosting CLI (create, list) and web UI: repo browser with
      commit-graph visualization, JSON/page/fragment content
      negotiation, read-only smart-HTTP cloning, systemd service.

 -- Markus Katharina Brechtel <brechtel@med.uni-frankfurt.de>  Wed, 15 Jul 2026 12:46:00 +0200
